<div id="c4">
<p>For #17-Why Not Socialism? by G.A. Cohen- is &#8220;all too-rate&#8221; (and, sadly, all-too-rate) a typo for &#8220;all-too-rare&#8221; or &#8220;all-too-late&#8221;? Reading anyone or about anything else I would just assume a typo for the first, but I&#8217;ve been thinking it is too late for the most ideal social order and the fight is going to have to be about how to down size the beast rather any (too easily co-optable) revolutionary happening.</p>

